{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x8ad86",
      "back_en": "Master Haku!? I BEG-YOU, a drink! A drink with",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Drunken slur and meaning preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8adb6",
      "back_en": "your CLOSE friend Maroro!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "BOSHOM/bosom rendered as slurred 'CHEGHO' (chegado); fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8ae3d",
      "back_en": "SUCH ill manner! Of COURSE I am here.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Slur style retained."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8aeb4",
      "back_en": "So it shall be!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8aec5",
      "back_en": "Now, MASTER Haku, thou shalt dr--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate, slur retained."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8b95d",
      "back_en": "The hapless-looking kid here is Haku,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8ba76",
      "back_en": "Now, now, dear LADY Nekone!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8babe",
      "back_en": "We merry spirits are in the very MIDST of a",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'merry lot' as 'alegres espíritos'; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8bae9",
      "back_en": "CELEBRATION. Let your face show only",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Reworded but meaning preserved across split."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8bb19",
      "back_en": "glowing smiles!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8bbf0",
      "back_en": "Urk--N-No, good lady, I meant...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dad5",
      "back_en": "Ah, how rare a sight it is, to see Mistress Nekone",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'tis' rendered as colloquial \"'tá\"; slightly odd but acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8db08",
      "back_en": "delighting thus in conversation.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8db57",
      "back_en": "Hers is a vast intellect, gifted with love",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8db86",
      "back_en": "by the Great Fathers, as befits one who bears",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dbb2",
      "back_en": "Kunneietai.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Proper noun unchanged."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dbbe",
      "back_en": "The vaunted imperial examination was like nothing",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dbf0",
      "back_en": "before her gifts. A scholar of philosophy so",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dc1f",
      "back_en": "young...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dc92",
      "back_en": "Incomparable. But one or two applicants per",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'in a decade' as 'por década'; fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dcc3",
      "back_en": "decade who seek the challenge conquer its",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dcef",
      "back_en": "travails.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dcf9",
      "back_en": "Mistress Nekone holds the honor of having bested",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dd2a",
      "back_en": "the beast at a more tender age than any",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dd55",
      "back_en": "other.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'before her' implied; meaning preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8ddb3",
      "back_en": "Naturally! Arduous was my journey, indeed,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dde5",
      "back_en": "but fate willed that I become a scholar.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'scholar true' as 'erudito'; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8de68",
      "back_en": "...Alas, Maroro is only an underscholar.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8de93",
      "back_en": "Meek and withered are my laurels before",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8debd",
      "back_en": "those of Mistress Nekone.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8df04",
      "back_en": "In truth, for such things to occur under",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Subjunctive reframed but meaning intact."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8df33",
      "back_en": "ordinary circumstance...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8df63",
      "back_en": "Bah, pay it no mind, prithee. Be not mistaken--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8df95",
      "back_en": "Mistress Nekone's is an intellect endowed with a spark",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dfc4",
      "back_en": "of genius.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8dfd6",
      "back_en": "Alas, it is both gift and curse. Her peers",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e007",
      "back_en": "shun her, aberrant as they perceive her mind to be.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e07d",
      "back_en": "None were able to comprehend the lofty matters",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e0ae",
      "back_en": "of which she spoke, so beyond their level was",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Truncated to match split; fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e0e5",
      "back_en": "In truth, it feels an age since I saw a smile",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'and longer' dropped but minor."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e114",
      "back_en": "so childlike upon her face.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate across split."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e2e5",
      "back_en": "She was too young, alas.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e2fe",
      "back_en": "Under ordinary circumstance, the mantle would",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Reordered across split; meaning intact."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e32e",
      "back_en": "have been proper for her. She was deemed too",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate across split."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x8e35b",
      "back_en": "young to receive it.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 45
